Package: worldcup26
Title: Access FIFA 2026 World Cup Schedule and Results
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sharon", "Machlis", , "smachlis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R wrapper for the football-data.org v4 API that retrieves
    team schedules and results for the 2026 FIFA World Cup. Provides
    helpers to list participating teams and to look up a team's full
    schedule, next match, or past results. Created with Claude Code and also checked with Codex.
